Package: splineClusterDetector
Type: Package
Title: Utilities for Cluster Detection and Significance Classification using Splines
Version: 1.0.0
Author: Luke Mullany, Howard Burkom
Maintainer: Luke Mullany <luke.mullany@jhuapl.edu>
Description: Provides utilities for manipulating time series of 
    location-based counts of events to detect geospatial clusters, and to determine the
    significance of these clusters using a set of simple spline models that classify based
    on the relationship between observed and the log(observed/expected) ratio of counts.
License: Apache License (>= 2)
Encoding: UTF-8
